The Orcskull MountainsAn alternate spelling or typo is shown as "Orcskill Mountains" in Dungeon Magazine #196. were a mountain range located on the island of Moray within the Moonshae Isles.
The mountains covered the southern tip of Moray. They were bordered on the east by the Strait of the Leviathan, and by the Trackless Sea to the south and west. The Shannyth River flowed north from the center of the Orcskull Mountains into central Moray.
The mountains were ruled by various tribes of orcs, ogres, giants, and other monstrous humanoids.
